CatDescriptText: Miss Patricia Samuels, 955 Rivermont Drive, Glen-Hazel Heights, was part of the "Pittsburghers Speak Up" column published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 16, 1957, pg. A1 with question: "Do you think that parents should be imprisoned for the unlawful acts of their children (under 18 years of age)?" answer reads: "No, because it's all in the child's mind, so far as what he or she wants to do."
